The '''Blue Dragon''', also known as '''Blue D''' or '''BLUE DRAGON'''<ref name="Enemy Identification Chart"/>, is an enemy in ''[[Final Fantasy]]''. It is a rare enemy that appears in the [[Mirage Tower]], as well as the [[Lifespring Grotto]] and [[Labyrinth of Time]] bonus dungeons in select releases. It is a [[Lightning (element)|lightning]] type enemy, resisting the element and often uses [[Thunderbolt (Final Fantasy)|Thunderbolt]] to deal [[Lightning (Final Fantasy)|lightning]] damage to the party. Blue Dragons have a very high [[Attack (command)|Attack]] stat and are moderately dangerous when the party first encounters it.

