== Etymology ==
{{Etym|Dragon}}

{{Etym|Chromatic dragon}} Blue dragons are the second-most powerful of the classic chromatic dragons. They excel in aerial combat, discharge lightning, are powerful at spell craft and adept at burrowing in sand.

